title: It's reasonable.
pid: de2c1969-792e-4068-b382-517456219ac4
body: |2-
  Perusing your own knowledge, whether on paper or in your head,
  is like a conversation. It can surprise you,
  make you laugh, make you furrow your brow.

  Tht's because the data navigator
  is aware of only a tiny fraction of that navigated.
